				<h1 class="mr-bottom-20">8 Lateral Head Tricep Exercises To Build Your Arms In 2025</h1>
								<div class="single-author mr-bottom-20">
					<div class="name-author">
						<div class="info">
							<div class="author-by" itemscope>
								<time class="updated has-small-font-size" datetime="2024-12-04T01:44:27-08:00"
									itemprop="dateModified">Updated on									December 04, 2024</time>
								<span class="has-small-font-size">- Writen by: </span>
								<span class="has-small-font-size" itemprop="author" itemscope
									itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a class="pri-color-2" target="_blank"
										href="https://www.endomondo.com/author/jason-spencer"
										title="View all posts by Jason Spencer ACSM PT, CSCS"
										rel="author" itemprop="url"><span class="ncustom has-small-font-size"
											itemprop="name">Jason Spencer ACSM PT, CSCS</span></a></span>
																	<span class="has-small-font-size"> - Reviewed by</span>
									<span class="has-small-font-size">
